## ğŸª› **3ï¸âƒ£ Circuit Connections**

| TMP36 Pin  | Connect To | Description                   |
| ---------- | ---------- | ----------------------------- |
| Left pin   | 5V         | Power supply                  |
| Middle pin | A0         | Sensor output (analog signal) |
| Right pin  | GND        | Ground                        |

**(Optional LED)**

| LED Leg               | Connect To     |
| --------------------- | -------------- |
| Long leg (anode +)    | Pin 13         |
| Short leg (cathode â€“) | Resistor â†’ GND |

âœ… Thatâ€™s it! Simple 3 connections â€” works perfectly in Tinkercad.

